OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,FA nursing student says he and his
OL,7,Fcohort were "sold a dream" as The
OL,8,FRoyal College of Nursing (RCN) Wales
OL,9,Fwarns that up to half of all nursing
OL,10,Fgraduates in Wales may not have a job
OL,11,Fto go to when NHS recruitment opens.
OL,13,FRCN Wales said it is "raising the
OL,14,Falarm" after confirmation that there
OL,15,Fis a shortage of Band 5 posts for
OL,16,Fnewly qualified nurses.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
