FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,FIt comes as recently graduated
OL,7,Fparamedics say they have been "left in
OL,8,Flimbo" after the Welsh Ambulance
OL,9,FService said it is "not in a position
OL,10,Fto employ newly qualified paramedics
OL,11,Fthis year".
OL,13,FOne student, Trystan Thomas, said he
OL,14,Ffelt "completely taken aback" upon
OL,15,Fhearing the news.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"We were sold a dream about becoming
OL,7,Fnurses, about becoming healthcare
OL,8,Fprofessionals - myself, paramedics, as
OL,9,Fwell as we've recently seen - and now
OL,10,Fwe've been told 'thanks for all your
OL,11,Fhard work, you may or may not get a
OL,12,Fjob,'" he told ITV News.
OL,14,F"We don't know what the future holds
OL,15,Fand we essentially feel like we're on
OL,16,Fstandby."
OL,18,FTrystan added that he has "never seen
OL,19,F(his cohort) so demoralised".
OL,26,@{D@Apm{D@Lpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"I used to walk in and see smiles and
OL,7,Fwe'd be happy about where we are. Now
OL,8,FI see long faces, me included."
OL,10,FRCN Wales said that the lack of jobs
OL,11,Ffor new nurses represents a "serious
OL,12,Ffailure of workforce planning and
OL,13,Fundermines the Welsh Government & NHS
OL,14,FDuty of Quality to improve the safety
OL,15,Fof care".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
