PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,FIt is calling on the Welsh Government
OL,7,Fto provide "urgent clarity on the
OL,8,Fscale of the shortfall, credible, long-
OL,9,Fterm workforce planning, and immediate
OL,10,Fsystemwide solutions to recruit,
OL,11,Fretain and deploy the nursing
OL,12,Fworkforce Wales needs both now and in
OL,13,Fthe future".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
