PN,46306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,FRCN Wales said it has received
OL,7,Fassurances that students will not be
OL,8,Fpenalised where posts are unavailable,
OL,9,Fincluding being released from any
OL,10,FworkinWales obligations and not
OL,11,Fbeing required to repay tuition fee
OL,12,Fsupport when workforce shortages
OL,13,Fprevent them from securing employment.
OL,15,FProfessor Sandy Harding, Associate
OL,16,FDirector of Nursing, RCN Wales, said:
OL,17,F"The situation facing newly registered
OL,18,Fnurses is deeply concerning and
OL,19,Fexposes serious failures in workforce
OL,20,Fplanning.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"It is becoming increasingly clear
OL,7,Fthat this situation is being driven by
OL,8,Ffinancial constraints, including the
OL,9,Ffreezing of vacant posts within the
OL,10,Flocal health boards.
OL,12,F"Our NHS is under intense pressure,
OL,13,Fyet hundreds of newly qualified nurses
OL,14,Fmay have no posts to enter. This is
OL,15,Fsimply unacceptable.
OL,17,F"These students stepped forward for
OL,18,FWales, trained through immense
OL,19,Fchallenges, and now face uncertainty
OL,20,Fat the very moment the system needs
OL,21,Fthem most. They deserve far better.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"Every newly qualified nurse will be
OL,7,Fvital to meeting Wales's care needs.
OL,8,FThe RCN will continue to demand
OL,9,Ftransparency, accountability and
OL,10,Flongterm planning from the system.
OL,12,F"We will not stop speaking up for
OL,13,Fstudents, for our safety critical
OL,14,Fnursing workforce, and for the people
OL,15,Fwho rely on safe, highquality care."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
