OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,FHealth Education and Improvement
OL,7,FWales, who coordinate the process in
OL,8,Fmatching medical students with
OL,9,Fvacancies, said the decision to
OL,10,Fpostpone the process of matching final-
OL,11,Fyear nursing students to jobs "had not
OL,12,Fbeen taken lightly".
OL,14,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"Student Streamlining is the
OL,16,Fnationally coordinated all-Wales
OL,17,Fprocess for matching final-year
OL,18,Fnursing, midwifery and Operating
OL,19,FDepartment Practitioner students to
OL,20,Fsuitable Band 5 roles across NHS Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"Following discussions across NHS
OL,7,FWales organisations and partners, the
OL,8,Fdecision has been taken to postpone
OL,9,Fthe opening of the nursing and
OL,10,Fmidwifery student streamlining process
OL,11,Ffrom 8 April to 11 May 2026.
OL,13,F"The extension has been agreed to
OL,14,Fallow additional time for Health
OL,15,FBoards to review workforce positions,
OL,16,Fconfirm and validate vacancies, and
OL,17,Fmaximise the number of roles available.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"This decision has not been taken
OL,7,Flightly. It reflects that NHS Wales
OL,8,Forganisations are managing a complex
OL,9,Ffinancial and operational position,
OL,10,Falongside other changes in the
OL,11,Favailable workforce including improved
OL,12,Fstaff retention in some areas. This
OL,13,Fmeans fewer Band 5 roles suitable for
OL,14,Fgraduates are currently available than
OL,15,Fin previous years.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"Whilst this extension is intended to
OL,7,Fincrease the number of available roles
OL,8,Ffor graduates, we cannot guarantee
OL,9,Fthat it will fully resolve the gap
OL,10,Fbetween the number of graduates and
OL,11,Favailable roles. In addition, while
OL,12,Fstreamlining aims to support fair and
OL,13,Fconsistent matching, it cannot
OL,14,Fguarantee a specific role or location.
OL,16,F"We understand this news is upsetting
OL,17,Ffor students who have shown dedication
OL,18,Fand commitment throughout their
OL,19,Ftraining.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"We also recognise that the NHS Wales
OL,7,Fbursary requirement to work in Wales
OL,8,Ffor two years after graduation may be
OL,9,Fcausing concern. While we're doing
OL,10,Feverything we can to help students
OL,11,Ffind jobs in NHS Wales we can release
OL,12,Fstudents from this requirement, at an
OL,13,Fappropriate time, if needed."
OL,15,FThe Welsh Labour Government said: "We
OL,16,Frecognise the strength of feeling
OL,17,Fexpressed by the Royal College of
OL,18,FNursing Wales and understand the
OL,19,Fconcern of nursing students and newly
OL,20,Fqualified nurses at this critical
OL,21,Fpoint in their careers.
OL,26,@wD@cOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"We are committed to ensuring that our
OL,7,Fsignificant investment in NHS
OL,8,Feducation and training is matched by
OL,9,Fmeaningful employment opportunities,
OL,10,Fand we do not underestimate the impact
OL,11,Fon individuals or on services if newly
OL,12,Fqualified nurses are unable to secure
OL,13,Fposts.
OL,15,F"We are working closely with Health
OL,16,FBoards, Health Education and
OL,17,FImprovement Wales (HEIW) and
OL,18,Funiversities to address these
OL,19,Fchallenges and support graduates.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"The number of nurses working in NHS
OL,7,FWales is now at record levels,
OL,8,Freflecting our continued investment in
OL,9,Fthe workforce. We are also seeing
OL,10,Ffalling vacancy rates and reduced
OL,11,Freliance on agency nursing, which are
OL,12,Fpositive indicators of progress in
OL,13,Fbuilding a more stable workforce.
OL,14,FHowever, we acknowledge that this
OL,15,Fimprovement must translate into clear
OL,16,Fand timely employment pathways for
OL,17,Fgraduates."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,FA Welsh Labour spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Fhugely value the work of nurses in our
OL,8,FNHS. The number of nurses working in
OL,9,FNHS Wales is now at record levels,
OL,10,Freflecting our continued investment in
OL,11,Fthe workforce.
OL,13,F"If re-elected, we will recruit, train
OL,14,Fand retain the staff our NHS needs
OL,15,Fthrough a long-term workforce plan. We
OL,16,Fwill widen access to medical education
OL,17,Fbased on The Open University's
OL,18,Fproposal for a flexible and blended
OL,19,Fmodel."
OL,26,@nD@cOUuD@AOU{D@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,FA Welsh Conservative spokesperson,
OL,7,Fsaid: "It is completely unacceptable
OL,8,Fthat newly qualified nurses could be
OL,9,Fleft without jobs at a time when our
OL,10,FNHS is under such intense pressure.
OL,12,F"Just last week we heard the deeply
OL,13,Fconcerning news that paramedic
OL,14,Fgraduates are also struggling to
OL,15,Fsecure roles, highlighting a clear and
OL,16,Fsystemic failure in workforce planning
OL,17,Fby the Welsh Labour Government.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46318
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"At a time when patients are facing
OL,7,Flong waits and staff are stretched to
OL,8,Fbreaking point, we should be doing
OL,9,Feverything possible to retain this
OL,10,Ftalent in our NHS, not forcing
OL,11,Fgraduates to look elsewhere.
OL,13,F"The Welsh Conservatives will retain,
OL,14,Frecruit and train more doctors,
OL,15,Fdentists, nurses, midwives and other
OL,16,Fhealth professionals to end Labour's
OL,17,Frecruitment crisis and improve access
OL,18,Fto appointments."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G18/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46319
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,FA Welsh Liberal Democrat spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is an extraordinary and
OL,8,Funforgivable failure by the Welsh
OL,9,FLabour Government.
OL,11,F"After years of mismanagement, we now
OL,12,Fhave the absurd situation where newly
OL,13,Fqualified nurses are left without jobs
OL,14,Fwhile patients are treated in
OL,15,Fcorridors and staff are pushed to
OL,16,Fbreaking point.
OL,18,F"Labour cannot keep blaming everyone
OL,19,Felse, this crisis is the direct result
OL,20,Fof their failure to plan, fund and
OL,21,Fstaff our NHS properly.
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G19/25
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
