OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46320
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"They must urgently guarantee jobs for
OL,7,Fnursing graduates and set out a
OL,8,Fserious workforce plan, or risk
OL,9,Fdriving away the very people our
OL,10,Fhealth service so desperately needs."
OL,12,FA Plaid Cymru spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"Despite the increasing pressures
OL,14,Ffacing the NHS and its workforce, with
OL,15,Fhuge numbers of nurse vacancies across
OL,16,FWales - the fact that there is a lack
OL,17,Fof available jobs for new nurses only
OL,18,Ffurther highlights Labour's serious
OL,19,Ffailure to invest in and forward plan
OL,20,Ffor the NHS workforce.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@eO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G20/25
