PN,46321
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1775675473
OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"A Plaid Cymru government will create
OL,7,Fa new comprehensive national workforce
OL,8,Fstrategy - ensuring our NHS staffing
OL,9,Fneeds are met, strategically align the
OL,10,Fprovision of courses with the demands
OL,11,Fwithin health boards, and ensure that
OL,12,Fstudents in Wales aren't forced to
OL,13,Fleave the country they planned to
OL,14,Fbuild their career.
OL,16,F"Plaid Cymru is the only party that
OL,17,Foffers new leadership for Wales with
OL,18,Freal plans to support our NHS after it
OL,19,Fhas been let down by Labour for so
OL,20,Flong."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G21/25
