OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Green Party
OL,7,Fsaid: "Following revelations about the
OL,8,FWelsh Government funding the training
OL,9,Fof paramedics and then not employing
OL,10,Fthem, we see the same clear failure of
OL,11,Fplanning regarding the training and
OL,12,Frecruitment of nurses. Labour's
OL,13,Fleadership of the NHS is a shambles
OL,14,Fwith no clear long-term workforce plan
OL,15,Fto match needs now and in the future.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G22/25
