OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"Nurses are the bedrock of our health
OL,7,Fcare system and Wales Green Party will
OL,8,Fensure workforce plans reflect the
OL,9,Fneeds of the health service and our
OL,10,Fchanging demographics. We will ensure
OL,11,Fthey are properly resourced with clear
OL,12,Fdelivery plans."
OL,14,FReform UK Wales said: "This situation
OL,15,Fis unacceptable and echoes what we've
OL,16,Fseen with the Welsh Ambulance Service.
