OL,3,CNursing graduates facing NHS job
OL,4,C'crisis', warns RCN Wales
OL,6,F"A lack of proper workforce planning
OL,7,Fby the Plaid-backed Welsh Labour
OL,8,FGovernment is making a mockery of
OL,9,Ftaxpayers who fund a substantial
OL,10,Fagency staff bill and training for
OL,11,Fnurses who aren't being offered jobs
OL,12,Fin the NHS.
OL,14,F"Reform UK Wales will implement a
OL,15,Fcomprehensive workforce review to
OL,16,Fquantify gaps and ensure that this
OL,17,Ffailure ends."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G24/25
